data.description: 5 bedroom, 4 Bath all brick custom with your own in-ground swimming pool! Deck off the kitchen for hanging out on for the summer pool days! Hardwood floors in formal Living Room/Office, formal Dining Room, Foyer, and Family Room. 1st floor Bedroom with adjacent full bath could be great for in-laws or guests. Kitchen with a breakfast bar and large eat-in area. Large laundry room. Master Bath has jetted tub and separate shower and walk in closest. All bedrooms are a great size! Extra large room over the garage! Extra concrete pad on the side of the house roughly 8 ft wide!
